  author =       "Antonio J. Rueda and Rafael J. Segura and Francisco R.
                 Feito and Juan Ruiz de Miras and Carlos Og{\'{a}}yar",
  URL =          "http://visinfo.zib.de/EVlib/Show?EVL-2004-122",
  abstract =     "Rasterization of polygons in 2D is a well known
                 problem, existing several optimal solutions to solve
                 it. The extension of this problem to 3D is more
