                 models. Independently of the decomposition method used
                 to approximate surfaces by polygons, an evaluation of
                 the surface at many parametric pairs is required to
                 generate meshes vertices. In this paper we give an
                 overview of the most important evaluation algorithms
                 and compare them regarding their runtime efficiency.
