                 updates a surface mesh model in real time by using
                 wavelet coefficients and height data decoded from a
                 compressed bitstream. To achieve this, a new mesh
                 approximation method using restricted quadtree
                 triangulation is designed on the basis of wavelet
                 coefficients representing surface complexity. Also, a
                 wavelet-based compression having a multiresolution
