  URL =          "http://visinfo.zib.de/EVlib/Show?EVL-2004-78",
  abstract =     "Practically every ray-casting based image synthesis
                 algorithm relies heavily on the tracing of shadow rays
                 to determine visibility between a sample point on a
                 light source and a surface point. If the light source
