  abstract =     "This paper presents a solution for the problem of
                 correspondence and relative orientation (RO) estimation
                 for a pair of images. The solution is obtained by
                 relaxation labeling using multiple metrics applied to
                 image primitives. Besides the use of metrics based on
                 radiometric elements (intensities, gradient, and
