                 constraint directly in the similarity and compatibility
                 computation. The proposed solution was applied to
                 synthetic and real images. The results showed that the
                 use of multiple metrics contribute to the automation of
                 the correspondence process and RO determination, even
                 considering pairs of images subject to convergence,
                 rotation, differences in scale, and presence of
                 repetitive patterns.",
